With Buildr
1. install buildr : gem install buildr
2. see the tests  : buildr test
3. play           : buildr chess:run

With Ant
1. install ant    : http://ant.apache.org/
2. see the tests  : ant test
3. play           : ant play

With Gradle
1. no need to install - simply use the Gradle wrapper (gradlew or gradlew.bat)
2. see the tests  : ./gradlew test
3. play           : ./gradlew play
